1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:02,680
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:02,680 --> 00:00:04,940
After being separated all 
of a sudden from Cana,

3
00:00:04,940 --> 00:00:07,770
I was thrown into a battle with one of 
the 7 Kin of Purgatory, Kain Hikaru.

4
00:00:07,770 --> 00:00:12,860
Natsu and I joined the battle halfway, but 
Natsu didn't really get a chance to shine.

5
00:00:12,860 --> 00:00:14,320
Oh, shut up!

6
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:18,040
But with the new special move I came up 
with, we raked a big white dumpling over the coals!

7
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:20,040
Special move, sure...

8
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:58,180
Pull harder!

9
00:01:58,180 --> 00:02:00,510
I'm pulling as hard as I can!

10
00:02:00,510 --> 00:02:02,160
Aye!

11
00:02:03,750 --> 00:02:08,010
And wait... Can't you just break 
the rocks with your fire, Natsu?

12
00:02:08,010 --> 00:02:09,300
Good thinking!

13
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,400
Jeez...

14
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:17,140
Light and darkness, mixed together...

15
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:24,960
The ones who will lead the way 
to the shining red tomorrow...

16
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,970
Fairies or Demons...

17
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:35,420
Whose hearts will it be?

18
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,980
Magic blades?

19
00:02:44,980 --> 00:02:46,930
She can summon weapons as well?

20
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,390
Go.

21
00:02:50,690 --> 00:02:53,460
Juvia's body is made of water!

22
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:55,020
No matter the attack, Juvia will not...

23
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,110
Juvia!

24
00:02:58,630 --> 00:03:02,840
Juvia's body made of water... was injured?

25
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:06,700
My blades attack the sense of pain directly.

26
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:09,240
In other words, they are "sensory blades".

27
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,420
That magic power...

28
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,540
I see.

29
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:14,690
You must be one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory.

30
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:16,710
I do not deem answering that as necessary.

31
00:03:17,230 --> 00:03:20,710
Wipe out the enemy. That is my mission.

32
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:26,230
Dead-End of Despair.

33
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,650
He's gone!

34
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:37,400
Zeref was here?

35
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,320
He's been taken away already!

36
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,340
What's with this smell?

37
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:44,480
She must have spread something around.

38
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,490
I can't follow her like this...

39
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:48,470
I've gotta search for Cana, too!

40
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,370
Why are you lifting your leg?

41
00:03:50,370 --> 00:03:52,100
Happy!

42
00:03:52,730 --> 00:03:55,490
Crap... Maybe I'll take a nap?

43
00:03:55,490 --> 00:03:56,520
Don't do that.

44
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,550
I'm worried about Cana too...

45
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,780
...but we have to go after Zeref now!

46
00:04:01,780 --> 00:04:04,180
Lucy-san, I'm sorry...

47
00:04:06,370 --> 00:04:08,010
It's like I just explained.

48
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:11,560
They're trying to use 
Zeref to change the world!

49
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:14,410
Change the world, huh?

50
00:04:14,850 --> 00:04:17,030
That's just way over-the-top.

51
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:20,580
I wanna live in a world 
that's just full of fish!

52
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:23,060
Um, it's not like that.

53
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:24,650
But see here...

54
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:27,200
I'm gonna make sure to finish this.

55
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:29,810
They hurt Gramps.

56
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:33,210
Those guys better not think 
I'll let them off this island.

57
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:35,560
Off the island?

58
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:40,030
That's it! They must have a ship somewhere!

59
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:44,300
That woman from before said something about 
bringing Zeref back to their master, right?

60
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:48,200
There's a good chance that their ship 
is anchored somewhere around here.

61
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,220
Zeref is being taken there!

62
00:04:50,220 --> 00:04:53,240
Happy, search for their ship from the sky!

63
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:58,730
Looks... like I'm out of magic power.

64
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:01,440
Then I guess you're just 
a widdle kitty cat...

65
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:05,930
In that case, how about we go back 
to where Wendy and Gramps is...

66
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,200
We can ask Carla and Lily.

67
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:15,630
This is Route E, where the first 
test of the exam took place.

68
00:05:22,690 --> 00:05:27,470
The grave of Mavis, the founding master 
of Fairy Tail, is somewhere in here.

69
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:29,800
I'll climb into first place.

70
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:31,660
I'll pass.

71
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:34,250
I'll become an S class wizard.

72
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:37,070
So I can see him...

73
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,730
So I can tell him...

74
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,990
...that I'm an S class wizard.

75
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,220
Light...

76
00:05:58,570 --> 00:06:02,330
Damn it, they never show up 
when you search for 'em...

77
00:06:02,330 --> 00:06:05,510
Where are these 7 Kin of Purgatory guys?

78
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:10,610
And that Cana sure was in a foul mood.

79
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:12,410
Did she run out of booze and...

80
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:14,470
Wait.

81
00:06:18,610 --> 00:06:23,790
Now that I think about it, I haven't seen 
her drink since we got to Tenroujima.

82
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:25,580
Is she going cold turkey?

83
00:06:31,330 --> 00:06:32,620
I sense someone...

84
00:06:33,850 --> 00:06:38,580
Soon, you'll return to being 
the true king, Zeref...

85
00:06:39,150 --> 00:06:42,900
Zeref? That man she's 
carrying on her shoulder?

86
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:53,900
Ul!

87
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:05,400
No... Grimoire Heart... She's my enemy!

88
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:12,670
She looks like her... Like my teacher, Ul.

89
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:19,730
Who the hell is she?

90
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:30,370
This is wondrous!

91
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:35,490
You seem to be in quite 
the good mood, old man.

92
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:42,770
3 of my 7 Kin of Purgatory 
have been defeated, it seems.

93
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:47,270
Those spawn of Makarov's 
have done quite well!

94
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:50,020
Then, is it my turn?

95
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:55,810
No, no... This is not a battle 
for you to join, Bluenote.

96
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:58,990
I would like to be able to 
play around a little bit.

97
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,410
I cannot let my body go soft.

98
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:19,140
Will you stop that?

99
00:08:21,210 --> 00:08:26,560
What? If I sink the ship, then they 
won't be able to find it, right?

100
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:29,550
It's better to expose them.

101
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:32,980
Makarov's brood will gather here,

102
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:36,570
unaware they've fallen 
inside the demon's maw...

103
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:41,080
Can't you eat any prey that 
hasn't been led into your mouth?

104
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,580
I will head out for my meal.

105
00:08:43,850 --> 00:08:46,100
You will stay here.

106
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:48,720
Where you go, the land will rage.

107
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,000
Stay calm.

108
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:54,800
The kids are down to four... Almost half.

109
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:59,050
If another falls... I'm heading out.

110
00:09:00,010 --> 00:09:02,020
Today seems like a day I 
can stretch my wings...

111
00:09:15,410 --> 00:09:17,520
Bluenote Stinger?!

112
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:21,530
The man who singlehandedly destroyed 
the Blue Dragon Regiment

113
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:24,060
led by Commander Ghora 
during the Cabria war...

114
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:28,960
The great wizard who is said not 
to even leave weeds in his wake...

115
00:09:29,340 --> 00:09:32,670
A big fish like that was in Grimoire Heart?

116
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:37,430
They are no longer an opponent 
that we can handle ourselves.

117
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:40,090
And the same goes for Fairy Tail, of course.

118
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:44,010
Let us contact headquarters at once.

119
00:09:44,410 --> 00:09:47,470
This is now beyond our purview.

120
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,510
Give me a little time.

121
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:52,780
What are you...?

122
00:09:54,610 --> 00:09:55,870
Dranbalt-sama!

123
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:58,820
He even took the communications 
lacrima with him!

124
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:01,410
We'll be late contacting headquarters now!

125
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:05,650
What in the world are 
you thinking, Dranbalt?!

126
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:12,610
Elsewhere in a corner of 
Tenroujima is Makarov,

127
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:17,160
who was gravely injured by 
Hades in a fierce battle.

128
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:23,940
Wendy, Lily, and Carla are looking after 
him, while waiting for Natsu to return.

129
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,890
Wendy!

130
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:30,350
Natsu-san!

131
00:10:30,350 --> 00:10:31,600
Lucy-san, too!

132
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,530
How's the Master doing?

133
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:36,730
I can't tell yet...

134
00:10:37,010 --> 00:10:39,660
His wounds are just too severe, I suppose.

135
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:43,250
But it's strange... I don't sense 
that his life is in danger.

136
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:47,880
Maybe there's some secret to this 
so-called "Sacred Ground"...

137
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:52,580
It's you!

138
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:55,370
Where'd you run off to, jerk?

139
00:10:55,370 --> 00:10:57,510
He's Mest, from the Magic Council.

140
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,300
My real name is Dranbalt.

141
00:11:00,730 --> 00:11:02,370
Dranbalt-san?

142
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:04,470
You don't need to worry, Wendy.

143
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:07,470
I've come to rescue you!

144
00:11:17,820 --> 00:11:23,740
With my magic, I can evacuate just the 
Fairy Tail members from this island.

145
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:27,030
If you can figure out where 
everyone is somehow...

146
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:31,180
Gonna have to pass on that.

147
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:36,750
Why do we have to ask the 
Magic Council to save us, huh?

148
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:41,220
This is a problem for our guild, and we're 
gonna deal with these guys ourselves.

149
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,680
That's not it!

150
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,350
If headquarters finds out what's going on,

151
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:47,750
there's a good chance 
they'll fire on the island!

152
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:51,070
They're gonna shoot Etherion again?!

153
00:11:51,070 --> 00:11:53,230
Don't you guys ever learn?

154
00:11:53,770 --> 00:11:56,110
Etherion? What's that?

155
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:58,610
I've heard rumors...

156
00:11:58,610 --> 00:12:01,760
It's some destructive magic 
that's seriously powerful.

157
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:05,580
It struck us while we were 
at the Tower of Heaven!

158
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:07,990
I-I'm impressed you're alive...

159
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:09,990
Well, a lot happened.

160
00:12:09,990 --> 00:12:14,960
I'm not sure of the details, but if 
I recall, lacrima absorbed it all.

161
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:19,070
This guild just faces crises 
wherever it goes, doesn't it?

162
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:21,820
If they fire that on us now...

163
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:24,640
We can't be sure what will happen, can we?

164
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:27,500
Then we just have to finish things up first.

165
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:32,490
Makarov's down! And Grimoire Heart 
still has fearsome people left!

166
00:12:32,490 --> 00:12:34,020
There's no way you can win!

167
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:37,660
Hey, now... So that's why you're 
gonna blow up the whole island?

168
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:40,490
This island is our guild's sacred ground!

169
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:42,770
The grave of the founding 
master is here, too!

170
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:45,360
I couldn't take you attacking this place...

171
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:47,670
I can't believe this!

172
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:51,010
If you do that, you won't get away with it!

173
00:12:51,330 --> 00:12:54,160
We're gonna protect the guild!

174
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:57,440
Trying to threaten us? The Magic Council?

175
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,950
You're just some wizard guild!

176
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:01,250
Now listen carefully, you!

177
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:05,590
I don't give a crap whether it's 
Grimoire Heart or the Magic Council.

178
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:09,530
Anyone who lays a hand on 
our guild is the enemy.

179
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:11,760
I'll destroy them all!

180
00:13:31,250 --> 00:13:34,790
This air... I feel a storm coming.

181
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:42,090
Juvia!

182
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:46,970
Putting aside the fact we used 
up our magic power for the exam,

183
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:50,930
I can't believe we're having such a 
hard time when it's two against one!

184
00:13:53,370 --> 00:13:54,520
Number 13.

185
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:57,540
Stand back. I will defeat her.

186
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:02,940
Erza Scarlet... You are number 4.

187
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:05,070
Number 4 of what?

188
00:14:05,690 --> 00:14:09,820
The fourth most important member 
to kill, by my reckoning.

189
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,620
Foolishness.

190
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:14,700
It is quite important.

191
00:14:17,930 --> 00:14:19,330
Why are you aiming for Juvia?!

192
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:21,950
Number 13 is weak trash,

193
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:23,540
so better to clean it up first!

194
00:14:26,050 --> 00:14:27,340
Juvia is...

195
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:29,420
Hang in there, Juvia!

196
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:35,210
Number 3 is Gildarts, but he no 
longer seems to be on the island.

197
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:39,390
Number 2 is Makarov, however he seems 
to have been defeated by Lord Hades.

198
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:41,600
The master is number 2?!

199
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:46,420
Are you saying there's someone 
more important than the master?

200
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:48,650
Number 1 is Gray.

201
00:14:49,890 --> 00:14:51,450
Gray Fullbuster!

202
00:14:51,450 --> 00:14:52,660
What?

203
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,330
Why Gray?

204
00:14:57,490 --> 00:15:01,730
He's... the man who killed Ultear's mother.

205
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:06,130
He caused Ultear to suffer!

206
00:15:06,870 --> 00:15:11,140
He's the man who hurt my Ultear!

207
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:14,510
I'll never forgive him! I'll 
tear him limb from limb!

208
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:15,720
Drat!

209
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:31,780
Never forgive?

210
00:15:33,490 --> 00:15:36,170
That is Juvia's line.

211
00:15:36,420 --> 00:15:41,510
Whose life were you planning to take, was it?

212
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:46,190
What's with her? She's only number 13.

213
00:15:46,190 --> 00:15:48,300
C-Calm down, Juvia!

214
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:54,460
Calm... down?

215
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:58,100
This woman is aiming for Gray-sama.

216
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:00,520
And for some irrational reason.

217
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:02,460
Um, but...

218
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:06,980
Do you think... Juvia can stay calm?

219
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:09,730
Juvia will never forgive this girl!

220
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:22,620
Water Nebula!

221
00:16:24,050 --> 00:16:25,040
Juvia...

222
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:29,670
She's like a totally different person 
than the one I fought during the exam.

223
00:16:32,330 --> 00:16:35,720
Her strong feelings for her 
loved one become her strength...

224
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:43,890
This is Juvia's true power...

225
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:47,350
Erza-san, please leave this to Juvia!

226
00:16:48,020 --> 00:16:51,540
Hurry and find Wendy and the 
others. And Gray-sama, as well.

227
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:54,740
Understood.

228
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,650
I'll leave this to you!

229
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:58,120
I won't let number 4 get away!

230
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,530
Maguilty Lese!

231
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:05,540
Water Slicer!

232
00:17:23,690 --> 00:17:25,230
It's raining...

233
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,690
Where are you headed?

234
00:17:28,520 --> 00:17:29,650
Their main camp?

235
00:17:30,250 --> 00:17:32,650
Where Grimoire Heart's master is?

236
00:17:40,390 --> 00:17:43,610
The tears put out of mind my own desires...

237
00:17:43,610 --> 00:17:46,720
The evil-eye wriggles 
impatiently in the darkness.

238
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,730
Is that from some song, Rusty?

239
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:50,420
Oh, no...

240
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,030
Just the scream of a shattered heart.

241
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:57,400
Azuma, you're quite beat up. For you.

242
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:01,500
Proof that I fought someone strong.

243
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:02,710
Someone strong?

244
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:07,020
That won't do at all. There isn't 
anyone like that in this guild.

245
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:11,150
My heart's fragment wavers not.

246
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:15,610
You mustn't underestimate Fairy Tail.

247
00:18:15,950 --> 00:18:18,930
Their weapon is not their magic power,

248
00:18:18,930 --> 00:18:21,570
but the ability to turn their 
conviction into a blade...

249
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:24,950
Conviction into a blade?

250
00:18:25,460 --> 00:18:28,060
Seems very much like our Meldy...

251
00:18:34,010 --> 00:18:35,190
Strange.

252
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:38,260
Even though it's the same human, Gray...

253
00:18:38,670 --> 00:18:40,700
One of us holds hatred,

254
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:42,350
and the other holds love.

255
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:47,720
Though it's the same person, the different 
feelings cause him to be seen differently.

256
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,550
It's natural.

257
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:50,880
A symbol of individuality.

258
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:52,510
It's what makes us human.

259
00:18:52,510 --> 00:18:54,190
I am lucky.

260
00:18:54,820 --> 00:18:57,570
I came here for the purpose of killing Gray.

261
00:18:58,160 --> 00:19:02,260
And I was able to meet with a person 
who feels strongly for Gray.

262
00:19:02,260 --> 00:19:03,290
What's that supposed to mean?!

263
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:07,520
Your feelings for Gray will kill him!

264
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:13,710
Juvia... I will show you a little bit 
of heaven, and a great sea of despair!

265
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,500
Now, think of him!

266
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:19,210
Picture the one you love...

267
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:24,060
Gray-sama...

268
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,660
There!

269
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:27,210
Sense Link!

270
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:40,690
What's this pain?

271
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:45,970
Lost Magic.

272
00:19:46,710 --> 00:19:48,330
Maguilty Sense!

273
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:51,340
W-What have you done?

274
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:55,000
Juvia and Gray's senses are now one.

275
00:19:55,900 --> 00:19:59,380
I can only connect them if one's feelings 
for the other is strong enough.

276
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:05,910
J-Juvia and Gray-sama are... one?!

277
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:07,220
Your senses, anyway.

278
00:20:08,930 --> 00:20:10,700
What is it now?

279
00:20:10,700 --> 00:20:12,850
I'm all light headed all of a sudden?

280
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,070
Feels good, doesn't it?

281
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:17,440
Your two senses are fully linked together.

282
00:20:18,540 --> 00:20:20,240
Juvia is in heaven!

283
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:22,090
Juvia will die in agony!

284
00:20:22,090 --> 00:20:25,990
But, this magic only shares pain!

285
00:20:34,070 --> 00:20:37,880
All the pain you experience is felt by Gray.

286
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,040
No...

287
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:42,480
You're trying to hurt Gray-sama?!

288
00:20:46,610 --> 00:20:47,610
Impossible...

289
00:20:48,140 --> 00:20:49,980
Her magic power continues to rise?

290
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,210
She was this powerful?

291
00:20:53,210 --> 00:20:54,940
Her feelings are giving her strength.

292
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:59,790
Then I'll show you the 
power of feelings myself!

293
00:21:00,190 --> 00:21:02,610
Three Spread Sense Link!

294
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:24,630
Why is Juvia hurt too?

295
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:28,970
W-What in the world?

296
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:43,370
If it's for Ultear... I don't 
need this life of mine!

297
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:48,990
I used you as a relay, and 
now I am linked to my target.

298
00:21:50,380 --> 00:21:56,640
Juvia, Gray, and my senses 
are all linked together.

299
00:21:57,230 --> 00:22:02,060
Now, no matter which one of 
us dies, Gray will die, too!

300
00:22:06,560 --> 00:22:08,970
This is the dead-end of despair.

301
00:22:10,370 --> 00:22:12,690
The dead-end of Gray's life!

302
00:23:55,860 --> 00:23:58,750
Love is a heart of affection.

303
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,380
What's wrong, Happy?

304
00:23:58,750 --> 00:24:02,140
Love is the feeling of wanting 
to protect someone dear to you.

305
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,540
Hey!

306
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:01,950
Hello?

307
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:03,770
Are you listening, Happy?

308
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:04,730
Love is an overflowing passion!

309
00:24:04,730 --> 00:24:10,230
The two, lead to a fateful encounter, their 
feelings deeply entwined, play a single tune together.

310
00:24:05,250 --> 00:24:06,900
I've got fish?

311
00:24:08,420 --> 00:24:09,950
Ooh, Carla's over there!

312
00:24:10,230 --> 00:24:13,470
Truly a love swimphony!

313
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,320
This isn't working.

314
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:12,670
His head's gone off somewhere.

315
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:16,910
Next time: Love and the Tears of Vigor.

316
00:24:16,910 --> 00:24:18,680
Screwed it up, Happy.

317
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:21,720
I-I didn't mispronounce it! I was 
just twalking wike a nwative!

318
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:25,160
Sure, fine, got it. Just slow down there.

319
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:27,390


